name: Start Your Engines!
Lore: 'Podracing is based on ancient contests that utilized animal-drawn carts. Today, Podracing''s reputation is known to be incredibly fast and dangerous.',
Text: 'LOST: Peek at top 3 cards of your Reserve Deck; place all but one in Lost Pile.STARTING: Deploy Podrace Arena (with a Podracer, opponent may also deploy a Podracer there), Boonta Eve Podrace, and any Effect that deploys for free. Place Interrupt in Reserve Deck.',
